sub_title: Student in Maastricht | Stiftung der Deutschen Wirtschaft | SEAL
summary: As a graduate student in the Research MSc European Studies at Maastricht University, I've honed my skills in strategic thinking, problem-solving, and teamwork. My exchange semester at Korea University exposed me to applied Machine Learning and Korean Diplomacy. With hands-on experience at NATO, leadership roles, and active involvement in diversity matters, I thrive in dynamic environments. Fluent in 5 languages, skilled in R, Python, and Java, and fueled by a keen interest in governance and AI, I'm ready to make a meaningful impact in EU security policy.
